# Data Deletion Request — Stokko

**Last Updated: May 30, 2026**

## Your Right to Delete Your Data
At Stokko, we respect your right to control your personal data.
You can request the deletion of your account and all associated
data at any time, even without having the app installed on your device.

---

## Option 1: Delete Directly from the App (Fastest)
1. Open the **Stokko** app.
2. Go to **Settings** (الإعدادات).
3. Tap your **profile card** at the top.
4. Select **"Delete Account"** (حذف الحساب).
5. Confirm the deletion.

✅ Your account and all associated business data will be permanently
   deleted immediately.

---

## Option 2: Submit a Deletion Request by Email
If you no longer have the app installed, send an email to:

**📧 [Insert Developer Email]**

### Subject line:
`Data Deletion Request — Stokko`

### Required information in the email:
- The email address linked to your Stokko account.
- Your request to permanently delete all your data.

⏱️ We will process your request and confirm deletion
   **within 7 business days**.

---

## What Data Will Be Deleted?
Upon confirmed deletion, the following will be permanently removed:

| Data Type | Deleted? |
|---|---|
| Firebase account (email, name) | ✅ Yes |
| Cloud-synced inventory data (VIP) | ✅ Yes |
| Cloud sales & customer records (VIP) | ✅ Yes |
| Local device data | ✅ Yes (on app uninstall) |

> ⚠️ **This action is irreversible.** Once deleted,
> your data cannot be recovered.

